ConnectionFactory<Connection>
public class SFEEConnectionFactory
extends java.lang.Object
implements ConnectionFactory<Connection>

This is an implementation of the com.collabnet.ccf.core.eis.connection.ConnectionFactory that will be used by the ConnectionManager to create, close and check if the connection is live and the session id is not invalid.
